'''Quaad Endac''' was a black marketeer and one of the prime movers on [[Varna Biqua]]. He was a mysterious individual, showing up only when it suited him (usually for high profit deals or for amusement value), and always in disguise. His most common appearances were as a young man, an older man, or an aged crone, but he once disguised himself as a [[Cerean/Legends|Cerean]]. The way he was typically identified was that he would wear a cutting of a [[ny'yosin bush]]. Endac was very serious while conducting business, and had no patience for those who cracked jokes.

